Core:
    AnimatorLoader              // loads animated layers & frames
    AnimatorManager             // do all work that requires KisNodeManager calls
    AnimatorSwitcher            // store current frame & switches it
    AnimatorUpdater             // updates image (after switching for example)
    AnimatorPlayer              // player
    AnimatorExporter            // exporter

Basic UI:
    AnimatorModel
    AnimatorView

Control UI:
    AnimatorActions
    AnimatorDock


Switching frame:
0) AnimatorManager::activate() or something else
1) AnimatorSwitcher::goFrame(new)
2) AnimatorSwitcher::frameChanged(old, new)
3) AnimatorUpdater::update(old, new)

After adding LightTable:
3) AnimatorLTUpdater::update(old, new)
